- masthead do
  %h1 Play Minecraft with your friends

  %p
    We've made it fast and easy.

  = link_to 'Start playing now for free', new_user_path, class: 'button'

#plans
  %table
    %thead
      %tr.name
        %th.casual Casual
        %th.hardcore Crafter
        %th.pro Pro
    %tbody
      %tr.price
        %td.casual $3.95 / mo
        %td.hardcore $7.95 / mo
        %td.pro $11.95 / mo
      %tr.hours
        %td.casual 40 hrs / mo
        %td.hardcore 80 hrs / mo
        %td.pro 160 hrs / mo
      %tr.worlds
        %td.casual 5 worlds
        %td.hardcore 10 worlds
        %td.pro 40 worlds

  %p It's <strong class="highlight">free</strong> for anybody to play for <strong class="highlight">#{pluralize User::FREE_HOURS, 'hour', 'hours'}</strong> a month in one world.


%ol#features
  %li.feature
    %h2 Zen Simplicity
    %p We do it all for you. No servers, RAM, Java or SSH. <strong>No more mumbojumbo</strong>. Just sign up and start playing, grasshopper.

  %li.feature
    %h2 Pay for yourself
    %p <strong>Don't pay for Frank</strong> who faked a sickie and played for a week straight. Sign up for a plan that suits <em>your</em> habits, not Frank's habit.

  %li.feature
    %h2 Show off
    %p We give you <strong>high quality maps</strong> of your worlds so you can quickly show your bros that rad 'coaster you've been working on.

  %li.feature
    %h2 Realtime in-game chat
    %p See when your friends are playing online and chat with them straight from the web. You don't have to open Minecraft to shout <strong>“OMG”</strong>.

  %li.feature
    %h2 Make love, not grief
    %p Keep pesky griefers out by only inviting <strong>people you trust</strong> to play with you.

  %li.feature
    %h2 Peace of mind
    %p Your pieces of art are <strong>continuously backed up</strong> in multiple locations. Never loose anything.

